	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Scanlines are literally the result of focused beams. Those horizontal lines are as you mentioned just a result of the phosphor layout, and aren't scanlines.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


